                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text pl-3">
                                        <p><a href="https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Lyon/@45.7579293,4.7650902,12z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x47f4ea516ae88797:0x408ab2ae4bb21f0!8m2!3d45.764043!4d4.835659" target="_blank"><span style="color: #5289D8">Address:</span><span style="color: #F9F190"> Lyon, France</span></a></p>
                                    </div>
